About 57% of the Russian car fleet are VAZ cars.[70]
In 2015, AvtoVAZ showed a negative gross margin in
ovaz_ifrs_fs_2015_eng.pdf). Analysts point to an increase in the cost of components and the devaluation of the ruble as the reasons for the company's unprofitability. Impairment losses and restructuring costs amounted to 42 billion rubles in 2015 against 4.7 billion rubles.